msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Duration` property is a float value indicating the length of "
"the transition in seconds. This is a Read-only property. This is calculated "
"by: End - Start. To modify duration, you must edit the :guilabel:`Start` and/"
"or :guilabel:`End` transition properties."
msgstr ""
